Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community,
Having regard to Council Directive 77/101/EEC of 23 November 1976 on the marketing of straight feedingstuffs (1), as last amended by Directive 86/354/EEC (2), and in particular Article 10 thereof,
Whereas Directive 77/101/EEC provides for amendment of the content of its Annex to take account of advances in scientific and technical knowledge;
Whereas it is appropriate to amend or supplement the provisions on the description and composition of certain by-products of rice milling or certain mineral substances in order to be able to identify them by their characteristics;
